headline: A Look At Targa Resources (TRGP) Valuation After Strong Recent Share Price Momentum
summary: Why Targa Resources (TRGP) is on investors’ radar Targa Resources (TRGP) has drawn attention after a strong recent share price move, with the stock up about 2.6% over the past week and around 21% over the past month. For investors tracking momentum in U.S. energy infrastructure names, that short term performance, alongside a total return around 11.6% over the past year as well as multi year gains, raises questions about how the current valuation lines up with company fundamentals.
